PostGIS setup:

more details can be found here:
https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/dev/ref/contrib/gis/install/geolibs/

$ sudo apt-get install binutils libproj-dev gdal-bin python-gdal gdal-bin libgeoip1
$ wget http://download.osgeo.org/geos/geos-3.3.8.tar.bz2
$ tar xjf geos-3.3.8.tar.bz2
$ cd geos-3.3.8
$ ./configure
$ make
$ sudo make install
$ cd ..
